name: Caprice Elise - Alone on the Bay
description: Caprice and I spent a couple of mornings in a row at the Bay Bluffs Park along Escambia Bay in Pensacola, Florida. Neither one of us lived there any longer but we both happened to be visiting at the same time so we took advantage of the coincidence to shoot some photos. Sunrise watchers and early morning joggers be damned. No fucks were given in the making of this photo:)
